tasks.description:
Edit `packages/schemas/src/common/media.schema.ts` (or create a new file `packages/schemas/src/common/media-upload.schema.ts`).

Add schemas:
- AdminUploadRequestSchema: { entityType: z.enum(['accommodation','destination','event','post']), entityId: z.string().uuid(), role: z.enum(['featured','gallery']) }
- DeleteMediaQuerySchema: { publicId: z.string().min(1).refine(s => s.startsWith('hospeda/')) }
- UploadResponseSchema: { url: z.string().url(), publicId: z.string(), width: z.number(), height: z.number() }

Export inferred types.

Tests: Schema validation tests for valid/invalid inputs (UUID format, enum values, publicId prefix).
